# npm lockfiles trigger full rebuilds and kill the Vite beforeDevCommand
**/package-lock.json
**/pnpm-lock.yaml
**/yarn.lock

# Frontend deps — Vite handles HMR; Rust watcher doesn't need these
../quartz-ui/node_modules/**

# Minecraft / mod logs during Play — tauri dev would restart and kill the window
logs/**
**/logs/**
